TypeDefinition

_result = createHashmapObject ["XPS_typ_AstarSearch",[_graph,_startKey,_endKey]]
Authors

Crashdome

Description

Traverses a HashmapObject which implements the XPS_ifc_IAstarGraph interface to find the best path.

_graph

XPS_ifc_IAstarGraph - the graph to perform the search on
